sources.title: Wyatt Earp Shoots First | Full Movie | Action Western
sources.description:
Wyatt Earp Shoots First - Wyatt Earp is one of the best lawman in the West and a first-rate gunfighter. But he is a conflicted individual who is haunted by what he was taught early in his career. Never, ever shoot first. But even a good man learns that sometimes, rules have to be broken to survive.
2019.  Stars: William Adams, Jezibell Anat, Meganiiq Barlet
